24  OptimalFanEfficiency(FanType const fanType, const double fanSpeed, const double flowRate, const double inletPressure,
25  const double outletPressure, const double compressibility)
26  : fanType(fanType), fanSpeed(fanSpeed), flowRate(flowRate), outletPressure(outletPressure),
27  inletPressure(inletPressure), compressibility(compressibility)
28  {};
29 
34  double calculate() {
35  FanTypeProperties const & currentFan = fanTypeProperties[static_cast<std::size_t>(fanType)];
36  double specificSpeed = (fanSpeed * std::sqrt(flowRate)) / (std::pow(outletPressure - inletPressure, 0.75)
37  * std::pow(compressibility, 0.25));
38 
39  if (specificSpeed < currentFan.minSpecificSpeed) {
40  specificSpeed = currentFan.minSpecificSpeed;
41  } else if (specificSpeed > currentFan.maxSpecificSpeed) {
42  specificSpeed = currentFan.maxSpecificSpeed;
43  }
44 
45  bool isPolynomial = specificSpeed < currentFan.transition;
46  if (isPolynomial) {
47  return currentFan.polynomialFunction(specificSpeed);
48  }
49  return currentFan.exponentialFunction(specificSpeed);
50  }
51 
52 private:
53  FanType const fanType;
54  const double fanSpeed, flowRate, outletPressure, inletPressure, compressibility;
55 
56 
57  struct FanTypeProperties {
58  private:
68  FanTypeProperties(const FanType fanType, const double transition, const double minSpecificSpeed, const double maxSpecificSpeed,
69  std::function<double (double n)> polynomialFunction,
70  std::function<double (double n)> exponentialFunction = [](double n) { return 0; })
71  : fanType(fanType), transition(transition), minSpecificSpeed(minSpecificSpeed), maxSpecificSpeed(maxSpecificSpeed),
72  polynomialFunction(std::move(polynomialFunction)), exponentialFunction(std::move(exponentialFunction))
73  {}
74 
75  const FanType fanType;
76  const double transition, minSpecificSpeed, maxSpecificSpeed;
77  const std::function<double (double n)> polynomialFunction;
78  const std::function<double (double n)> exponentialFunction;
79  friend class OptimalFanEfficiency;
80  };
